page.title: 11SWAFFHAM BULBECK SCHOOL
page.content: Our school was built in 1840 it has 3 classrooms and 1 mobile classroom. there are about 80 children. There are 3 fulltime teachers and a part time teacher.Other adults come in to help. We have a video and two computers and a lot of things to go with the computer. We have a big playground with a field and P.E. shed. Our 3rd classroom is a library and study area. We have lots of art things and a whole trolley full of musical instruments. We also have stick insects which we look after.
